steps.name: Given I open the login page
And I login with email and password
Given user go to Inventory page
And user click tambah produk button
And user choose Tambahkan secara manual
Then user will redirect to Tambah Produk Baru page
assert expected **'<span.text-xl.font-bold>'** to contain text **'Tambah Produk Baru'**
assert expected **[ <img.cursor-pointer.mb-5>, 4 more... ]** to have attribute **src**
assert expected **<input.grow.w-full.bg-transparent.outline-none.undefined>** not to have value **''**
And user choose Segmen Produk FMCG
assert expected **<input.grow.w-full.bg-transparent.outline-none.undefined>** to have value **Minuman - Air Mineral**
assert expected **<div#react-select-2-placeholder.absolute.left-[0px].py-2.text-gray-500.css-1vlsb4t-placeholder>** to have text **e.g. PCS**
And user click Tambah Unit baru
assert expected **[ <div.flex-1.text-lg.text-gray-800.font-bold>, 1 more... ]** to contain text **Tambah Unit**
And user input jumlah dalam unit terkecil
Then user click simpan tambah unit
